OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FA suspected gunman who allegedly
OL,7,Fdubbed himself a "Friendly Federal
OL,8,FAssassin" before storming a White
OL,9,FHouse event with guns and knives is
OL,10,Fdue to appear in court on Monday.
OL,12,FCole Tomas Allen, 31, is facing
OL,13,Fcharges of using a firearm during a
OL,14,Fcrime of violence and assaulting a
OL,15,Ffederal officer with a dangerous
OL,16,Fweapon, the acting US attorney for
OL,17,FWashington DC, said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
