OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FShots were fired in the lobby of the
OL,7,FWhite House Correspondents' Dinner at
OL,8,Fthe Washington Hilton Hotel on
OL,9,FSaturday evening, causing US President
OL,10,FDonald Trump and his wife Melania, to
OL,11,Fbe rushed to safety by Secret Service
OL,12,Fagents.
OL,14,FAn officer who was shot and injured
OL,15,Fduring the incident was wearing a
OL,16,Fbulletproof vest and has since been
OL,17,Fdischarged from hospital, according to
OL,18,Fthe Secret Service's chief of
OL,19,Fcommunications.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
