OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FTrump described the suspect as
OL,7,F"probably a pretty sick guy" during an
OL,8,Finterview on Sunday, adding that he
OL,9,Fwas "not worried" during the attack.
OL,11,FHere's everything we know about the
OL,12,Falleged attacker so far.
OL,14,FWho is Cole Tomas Allen?
OL,16,FAllen is a part-time teacher and
OL,17,Famateur video game developer from
OL,18,FTorrance, a city in the Los Angeles
OL,19,Fregion of California.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
