OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FHe graduated with a degree in
OL,7,Fmechanical engineering from California
OL,8,FInstitute of Technology in 2017, and
OL,9,Flater went on to gain a master's in
OL,10,Fcomputer science at California State
OL,11,FUniversity, according to his LinkedIn
OL,12,Fprofile.
OL,14,FAs a student, he was featured in a
OL,15,Flocal news report for developing an
OL,16,Femergency brake prototype for
OL,17,Fwheelchairs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
