OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FHe published an indie game called
OL,7,FBohrdom - a "skill-based, non-violent
OL,8,Fasymmetrical fighting game" - for
OL,9,Fpurchase on Steam after registering a
OL,10,Ftrademark for its name in 2018,
OL,11,Faccording to federal trademark records.
OL,13,FAllen worked for C2 Education, which
OL,14,Fspecialises in college test
OL,15,Fpreparation, and appeared to have been
OL,16,Fawarded "teacher of the month" by C2's
OL,17,FTorrance office in December 2024,
OL,18,Faccording to a post on his Facebook
OL,19,Fpage.
OL,26,@oD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
