OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FA group of high school students
OL,7,Ftutored by Allen shared a statement
OL,8,Fvia the Asian American Civic Trust,
OL,9,Fwhich described him as "generally very
OL,10,Fintelligent" and "normal and friendly".
OL,12,FAllen contributed $25 to a Democratic
OL,13,FParty political action committee in
OL,14,Fsupport of Kamala Harris for president
OL,15,Fin 2024, according to federal campaign
OL,16,Ffinance records.
OL,18,FWhat is his alleged motive?
OL,26,@rD@LO]rD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
