OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FAllen sent a document to family
OL,7,Fmembers ten minutes before the
OL,8,Fshooting occurred, signing it off as
OL,9,F"Cole 'coldForce' 'Friendly Federal
OL,10,FAssassin' Allen", authorities said.
OL,12,FIn the note, he allegedly wrote he was
OL,13,F"no longer willing to permit a
OL,14,Fpaedophile, rapist, and traitor to
OL,15,Fcoat my hands with his crimes",
OL,16,Fstating that Trump administration
OL,17,Fofficials - excluding FBI director
OL,18,FKash Patel - were the targets.
OL,26,@rD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
