OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FDiscussing whether he should "turn the
OL,7,Fother cheek" as a Christian, the
OL,8,Fdocument said: "Turning the other
OL,9,Fcheek when *someone else* is oppressed
OL,10,Fis not Christian behaviour; it is
OL,11,Fcomplicity in the oppressor's crimes."
OL,13,FAuthorities are reviewing the
OL,14,Fstatement and speaking to Allen's
OL,15,Ffamily members to learn more about his
OL,16,Fmotive, Acting US Attorney General
OL,17,FTodd Blanche told ITV News' US partner
OL,18,FCNN.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
