OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"We're still looking to try to
OL,12,Funderstand a motive. From our
OL,13,Fpreliminary investigation, it does
OL,14,Fappear the suspect was targeting
OL,15,Fmembers of the administration,"
OL,16,FBlanche said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
