OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FAllen both apologised to and thanked
OL,7,Fhis family, friends, colleagues and
OL,8,Fstudents in the document, and claimed
OL,9,Fhe had faced a lack of security in
OL,10,Fpreparing for the alleged attack.
OL,12,F"I walk in with multiple weapons and
OL,13,Fnot a single person there considers
OL,14,Fthe possibility that I could be a
OL,15,Fthreat," the note said.
OL,17,FIt ended with Allen appearing to make
OL,18,Flight of his future arrest, stating
OL,19,Fthat he felt "awful" and wanted to
OL,20,F"throw up" ahead of the alleged
OL,21,Fshooting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
