SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777345462
OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,F"I want to cry for all the things I
OL,7,Fwanted to do and never will, for all
OL,8,Fthe people whose trust this betrays; I
OL,9,Fexperience rage thinking about
OL,10,Feverything this administration has
OL,11,Fdone," the note said.
OL,13,F"Can't really recommend it! Stay in
OL,14,Fschool, kids."
OL,16,FWhat has Allen been charged with?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
