OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FAllen will face charges of using a
OL,7,Ffirearm during a crime of violence and
OL,8,Fassault on a federal officer, as well
OL,9,Fas other potential counts, authorities
OL,10,Fhave said.
OL,12,FHe has not previously been charged
OL,13,Fwith any crimes, a search of state and
OL,14,Ffederal court databases shows.
OL,16,FAllen was taken to a local hospital
OL,17,Fafter the shooting and is expected to
OL,18,Fbe charged in a federal court on
OL,19,FMonday.
OL,21,FWhat have his family said?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
