OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FAllen's sister, who lives in Maryland,
OL,7,Ftold investigators her brother was
OL,8,Fprone to making radical statements, an
OL,9,Fanonymous official told the Associated
OL,10,FPress.
OL,12,FShe told investigators her brother had
OL,13,Flegally purchased several weapons from
OL,14,Fa California gun store and kept them
OL,15,Fat their parents' home in Torrance
OL,16,Fwithout their knowledge, the official
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
