OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FThe White House initially told CNN
OL,7,FAllen's brother had notified the New
OL,8,FLondon Police Department of the
OL,9,Falleged manifesto before the incident,
OL,10,Fbut an official has since said they
OL,11,Fare still trying to clarify the
OL,12,Ftimeline.
OL,14,FWhat has Donald Trump said?
OL,16,FDuring an interview with CBS News on
OL,17,FSunday, the US president said he
OL,18,F"wasn't worried" about the shooting,
OL,19,Ftelling journalist Norah O'Donnell: "I
OL,20,Funderstand life. We live in a crazy
OL,21,Fworld."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777345462
OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,FWhen O'Donnell read out a part of
OL,7,FAllen's alleged manifesto referencing
OL,8,Fa "paedophile, rapist, and traitor",
OL,9,FTrump responded angrily and said the
OL,10,Fsuspect was a "sick person".
OL,12,F"I'm not a rapist. I didn't rape
OL,13,Fanybody. I'm not a paedophile," Trump
OL,14,Fsaid, telling O'Donnell she was
OL,15,F"disgraceful" and should be ashamed of
OL,16,Fherself for reading the note out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777345462
OL,3,CWhat we know about 'teacher of the
OL,4,Cmonth' suspect in Washington shooting
OL,6,F"You read that crap from some sick
OL,7,Fperson? I got associated with all
OL,8,Fstuff that has nothing to do with me.
OL,9,FI was totally exonerated," the
OL,10,Fpresident continued.
OL,12,FIn the hours immediately after the
OL,13,Fshooting, Trump praised the "fantastic
OL,14,Fjob" of the Secret Service and US law
OL,15,Fenforcement in a post on Truth Social.
OL,17,F"They acted quickly and bravely. The
OL,18,Fshooter has been apprehended, and I
OL,19,Fhave recommended that we 'LET THE SHOW
OL,20,FGO ON' but, will entirely be guided by
OL,21,FLaw Enforcement," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
